  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>Levi Apartments are self catering and provide you with a well equipped and spacious kitchen. The apartment complex is situated close to the local supermarket and you'll find local bars and restaurants nearby if you would like to dine out in the evening. </p>
<p>Optional half board upgrade at the Levi Hotel Spa. You'll have breakfast here, plus a three course buffet-style dinner is taken in the Ahku restaurant in the main hotel building. </p>
<p>A Festive Feast included for all guests during December, for a Christmas celebration with games and music. Please also note that the Festive Feast replaces the last dinner included in the half-board option. </p>]]></cateringDescription>
  <deactivateThisPage>0</deactivateThisPage>
  <description><![CDATA[<p>Brand new to Inghams, the modern, Scandi style Sirus and Orion Apartments, are ideal for couples, small families or groups of friends. Located in the centre of <a data-udi="umb://document/1b2fbafe6b3546cbbcb8a26241bb809c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/1b2fbafe6b3546cbbcb8a26241bb809c}" title="Levi">Levi</a> resort, you'll be right next to the ski area which is a only a short walk away - not only that but you'll have easy access to a range of winter excursions, local bars and restaurants.</p>
<h2>Modern design  </h2>
<p>If you'd like to add a touch of luxury to your winter holiday, then these apartments are the perfect choice. Both the Siruis and Orion apartments are finished to a very high standard and incorporate modern décor with cosy wooden features. </p>
<h2>Facilities</h2>
<p>Everything you need for an active winter break or ski trip is under one roof with your own drying cabinet and access to a communal ski maintenance room. We love that there's a private sauna in each apartment - nothing beats it after a day out exploring in the Arctic. </p>]]></description>
